Certificate, the Seller will no longer be a beneficiary of the
Issuer, except to the extent that the Seller is a
Certificateholder.

SECTION 3.2.Â  Authorization
of the Certificates .Â Concurrently with the sale of the
Transferred Assets to the Issuer pursuant to the Sale and Servicing
Agreement, at the direction of the Seller, (a) a single Book-Entry
Certificate shall be executed by the Owner Trustee on behalf of the
