in the name of Cede & Co. or (b) a single Definitive
Certificate shall be executed by the Owner Trustee on behalf of the
Issuer and authenticated and delivered by the Certificate Registrar
to or upon the written order of the Seller.Â The Certificate
shall represent 100% of the Percentage Interest in the Issuer and
shall be fully paid and nonassessable.

SECTION 3.3.Â  Book-Entry
Certificates .

(a) The Certificate, upon original
